    RHODS -.->|"gateway API<br/>CONDITIONAL"| GatewayAPI[Gateway API v1]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (Deploys/Manages)
    RHODS -->|"deploys/manages"| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    RHODS -->|"deploys/manages"| KServe[KServe Operator]
    RHODS -->|"deploys/manages"| Pipelines[Kubeflow Pipelines]
