    RHODS -->|"deploys/manages"| ModelController[Model Controller]
    RHODS -->|"deploys/manages"| Feast[Feast Operator]
    RHODS -->|"deploys/manages"| LlamaStack[Llama Stack Operator]
    RHODS -->|"deploys/manages"| Kueue[Kueue]

    %% Integration Points
    RHODS -->|"CRD API<br/>6443/TCP"| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    RHODS -->|"OLM API"| OLM[Operator Lifecycle Manager]

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|"scrapes metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS"| RHODS
    OpenShiftMon[OpenShift Monitoring] -->|"federation<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS"| Prometheus

    %% External Services
    RHODS -->|"image pulls<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"| ImageReg[Image Registries<br/>quay.io, registry.redhat.io]

